arely ate to their fill","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 15, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The family of Muhammad, peace and blessings be upon him,\u00a0never ate to their fill of wheat bread for three consecutive nights, ever since they had come to Medina, until he passed away. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6089, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2970 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15362,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/24\/seeing-muhammad-in-your-dreams\/","url_meta":{"origin":37913,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Visions: Seeing the Prophet in your dreams","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever sees me in a dream has truly seen me, for Satan cannot imitate me.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6994, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2266 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2509,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/24\/prophet-face-like-qamar\/","url_meta":{"origin":37913,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: The Prophet&#8217;s face was like the Moon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ishaq reported: A man asked Al-Bara', may Allah be pleased with him, \u201cWas the face of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, like a sword?\u201d Al-Bara' said, \u201cNo, it was like the moon.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3552 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0625\u0650\u0633\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0642\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064f\u0626\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33014,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/what-to-say-final-tashahhud\/","url_meta":{"origin":37913,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: What to say at end of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b ibn \u2018Urjah reported: We asked, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how do we send blessings upon you and the people of the house? Allah has taught us how to send peace upon you.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSay: O Allah, send grace upon Muhammad and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes"